:UNSET_VERBOSE
:: Unset VERBOSE before exiting each sub-routine.
:: and force echo off
@if NOT defined DEBUG (
  @set VERBOSE=
  @echo off
)
@goto :EOF
::===UNSET_VERBOSE================


